3️⃣ Write a shell script to check whether a number is even or odd
Code:
#!/bin/bash
echo "Enter a number:"
read num

if [ $((num%2)) -eq 0 ]
then
    echo "Even number"
else
    echo "Odd number"
fi
4️⃣ Write a shell script to find the factorial of a number
Code:
#!/bin/bash
echo "Enter a number:"
read num

fact=1

for ((i=1; i<=num; i++))
do
    fact=$((fact*i))
done

echo "Factorial = $fact"
5️⃣ Write a shell script to check if a number is positive, negative or zero
Code:
#!/bin/bash
echo "Enter a number:"
read num

if [ $num -gt 0 ]
then
    echo "Positive"
elif [ $num -lt 0 ]
then
    echo "Negative"
else
    echo "Zero"
fi
