🔟 Write a shell script to find the largest of three numbers
Code:
#!/bin/bash
echo "Enter three numbers:"
read a b c

if [ $a -ge $b ] && [ $a -ge $c ]
then
    echo "Largest = $a"
elif [ $b -ge $a ] && [ $b -ge $c ]
then
    echo "Largest = $b"
else
    echo "Largest = $c"
fi
